data.description: Master on Main in Harrison School District! Superior Curb Appeal with Stone Front and Level Driveway. This 5BR, 4.5BA Home with Finished Basement has an Open Concept Floor Plan with 8 Foot Doorways & 10 Foot Ceilings. The Two Story Foyer, French Doors & Plantation Shutters welcome you. Beautiful Hardwoods and Tile Flooring Throughout. Spacious Two Story Family Room with Ceiling High Stone Fireplace, Built-ins and Great Natural Light. Gorgeous Kitchen features Quartz Counters, Tile Backsplash and Stainless Appliances including Double Ovens & Built-in Microwave. Large Peninsula Island with Custom Pendant Lighting and Under Cabinet Lighting. Separate Dining Room & Breakfast Area. Main Level also has a Formal Sitting Room/Den Perfect for Home Office. Oversized Owner's Suite boasts French Doors leading to Deck. Master Bath includes Frameless Glass Tile Shower, Soaking Tub and Double Vanity. Hardwood Stairs and Iron Spindles lead you the Second Floor with 3 Additional Large Bedrooms/Closets and 2 Full Baths including Jack/Jill Setup. Room to Grow in the Full Finished Daylight Basement including In-Law/Teen Suite. Kitchenette has Granite Countertops, Full Sink, Cabinets & Fridge. In addition, there's a 5th Bedroom, Full Bath, Recreation Area and HUGE Unfinished Storage Room that includes a Tall Safe. Walk-in Laundry Room adjacent to garage with Mud Sink, Hall Tree & Cabinets. Very Large and Private Fenced Backyard. Deck spans across the ENTIRE Back of the House with Entry Points from Family Room, Den & Master BR. Home has Smart Switches & Dimmers installed. Level 2 EV Charger. All New Gutters with Back Gutter Guards. 2021 Main Level/Upstairs HVAC Systems. 2021 Water Heater. The Backyard has Neighborhood Approval and Room for an Inground Pool. Chestatee Creek is a Manicured Community Convenient to Shopping, Dining, etc. Full 3D Tour with QR Code at end of pics!
